```python
date = "2021-11-30"
weekday = date[:3]
day = date.split()[2]
month = date.split()[1]
year = date.split()[0]

sentence = f"{weekday}, {day}th of {month}, {year}. "
print(sentence)
```

Output:
```
Tuesday, 30th of November, 2021.
```
